17. Rhe1
{ 17.h4 ?  a4  18.Ba2  Rxc2 !  19.Qxc2   19.Kxc2 ?  Bf5+  (Rc8 favors Black as White's queen is exposed and his pawns are weak.)   17.g4  Rc7  followed by  Rfc8  gives Black good counterplay. }
